n el \u00c1rea de Control P\u00fablico, mediante controles vehiculares desarrollados con total normalidad.","body":"Se llev\u00f3 a cabo un operativo de saturaci\u00f3n y alta visibilidad, en trabajo conjunto con el \u00c1rea de Control P\u00fablico, mediante controles vehiculares desarrollados con total normalidad.\r\n\r\nDurante el procedimiento no se registraron infracciones en los veh\u00edculos chequeados.\r\nDel operativo particip\u00f3 personal policial de San Vicente y Colonia Margarita, reforzando las tareas de prevenci\u00f3n y control en la v\u00eda p\u00fablica.\r\n\r\nEstas acciones forman parte del trabajo articulado para fortalecer la seguridad, la prevenci\u00f3n y el orden en nuestra comunidad.","more_info":null,"landmark_id":null,"event_id":null,"published_from":"2026-03-16T03:00:00.000000Z","published_to":"2027-03-16T03:00:00.000000Z","is_important":true,"created_at":"2026-03-17T15:50:59.000000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-17T15:55:38.000000Z","deleted_at":null,"categories":[{"id":14,"name":"Control P\u00fablico","category_id":null,"external_id":null,"created_at":"2026-03-17T15:14:01.000000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-17T15:14:01.000000Z","pivot":{"categorizable_id":13,"category_id":14,"categorizable_type":"App\\Models\\News"}}],"landmark":null,"images":[{"id":63,"name":"654113774_18362148646200974_5310069730536382777_n.jpg","url":"https:\/\/api-sanvicente.vecino.digital\/storage\/images\/JGrWq843AHeTLoWVosytxtDlM1Vkqbuvdcc4o8lw.jpg","path":"images\/JGrWq843AHeTLoWVosytxtDlM1Vkqbuvdcc4o8lw.jpg","type":"image","order":1,"mediable_type":"App\\Models\\News","mediable_id":13,"created_at":"2026-03-17T15:54:30.000000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-17T15:54:30.000000Z"},{"id":64,"name":"652900188_18362148655200974_6861473317462933961_n.jpg","url":"https:\/\/api-sanvicente.vecino.digital\/storage\/images\/yP61O8bcElUBfic5OBJCLfKZ6PL1CMj0WUNC6jId.jpg","path":"images\/yP61O8bcElUBfic5OBJCLfKZ6PL1CMj0WUNC6jId.jpg","type":"image","order":1,"mediable_type":"App\\Models\\News"